{"tid":1538684,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警 你地而家係唔係好驚呢","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:35:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T15:45:40.000Z","uid":10691,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"674bf53ed21630fb8fb36f2490c721367202a05d","tid":1538684,"uid":10691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:35:29.000Z","msg":"林鄭而家肯撤回 唔難保之後就清算你呢d殺人犯<br />\n你要明白你地係condom 黎㗎咋<br />\n上面要收你皮幾時都得呀 <br />\n你慢慢係白色恐佈入面懺悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d970dc0b47691bc0fc9089bcabcf4ec412a71c17","tid":1538684,"uid":10691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e929cf13e25587c8f432ee6b3316104bb2f2242","tid":1538684,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:35:38.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dcd829e6dd51f005fbdd49c3263f7e6374a8672","tid":1538684,"uid":10691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:35:45.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"7a817d04f0400b2802519a0e06e9d8332413fe76","tid":1538684,"uid":10691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:35:58.000Z","msg":"三"},{"pid":"d0a1c91ba277083b71b2937f8bb1a4360a02eef1","tid":1538684,"uid":10691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:36:08.000Z","msg":"Four"},